- PASCAL VOC - http://host.robots.ox.ac.uk/pascal/VOC/
- COCO - http://cocodataset.org/
- YOLO9000 - https://arxiv.org/abs/1612.08242
- YOLO4 - https://arxiv.org/abs/2004.10934v1

